{"tid":1111202,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[電影撚入] master 讀電影有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-04-16T23:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T15:35:14.000Z","uid":143672,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"25a3671f868095253a77d8be69078a36741ea7fb","tid":1111202,"uid":143672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"本身大學major係econ，minor緊psych<br />\n由細到大都對電影好有興趣，好想做導演/編劇<br />\n但好衰唔衰大學又揀左個唔關事既major <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連minor都唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近見到淪落人個導演原來大學都係讀緊啲唔關事嘅嘢，係master 先讀番電影<br />\n<br />\n想問下如果好似我咁從來冇接觸過任何關於電影嘅學術嘢，做幾年嘢儲下錢後半工讀電影有冇得諗？出路如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好想可以做啲自己真正有興趣嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚後悔揀左econ呢啲垃圾科</span>"},{"pid":"3e635816f4f2a28fbecb0af49d23ee09f9b2a325","tid":1111202,"uid":143672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351bcfde6a344bef49976724e230287e1ac49b8b","tid":1111202,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:20:20.000Z","msg":"會窮"},{"pid":"73be7ea4cd938364c1767e8ccfc807c9355895ad","tid":1111202,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:20:26.000Z","msg":"讀完冇出路"},{"pid":"cd554b30f0466b44a3f9171fca8ad07661bf4a2a","tid":1111202,"uid":143672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:20:41.000Z","msg":"唔一定要做到導演咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要係關電影事嘅工就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7322848aaf943e19c2ae445b87bc0f37c1e0ea0d","tid":1111202,"uid":143672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"